00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:47.501
I'm sure you know what you're doing.

00:10:48.252 --> 00:10:51.255
It's my younger brother's marriage,
so see to it personally.

00:11:01.390 --> 00:11:05.019
A military clan from Goryeo?
I wonder what they're doing now.

00:11:05.102 --> 00:11:08.314
They must be growing rice
somewhere in the countryside.

00:11:08.397 --> 00:11:11.942
What a sly fox you are.

00:11:12.026 --> 00:11:14.320
If I'm a fox, what are you, Geum-nok?

00:11:15.446 --> 00:11:16.864
GEUM-NOK
SUK-YONG

00:11:16.947 --> 00:11:19.825
