00:11:34.340 --> 00:11:35.382
Your Majesty.

00:11:37.218 --> 00:11:39.261
SHIN YEO-GYEONG
QUEEN CONSORT

00:11:39.345 --> 00:11:42.932
I hear my niece and
the Chief Secretary's son got engaged.

00:11:43.015 --> 00:11:43.933
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:11:44.016 --> 00:11:47.102
The Im family is seeking to expand
its influence through marriage ties.

00:11:48.646 --> 00:11:51.565
Everyone knows their scheme,
yet there is no one to stop it.

00:11:51.649 --> 00:11:53.150
It is truly grievous.

00:11:54.944 --> 00:11:55.986
Oh, Geum-nok!

00:12:01.158 --> 00:12:03.661
It tickles, Your Majesty!

00:12:05.204 --> 00:12:06.872
I am deeply sorry

00:12:07.581 --> 00:12:10.000
