keep befalling Your Majesty.

00:12:11.126 --> 00:12:13.045
But please do not be disheartened.

00:12:13.128 --> 00:12:16.340
My son will will look after your niece

00:12:16.423 --> 00:12:18.592
with the greatest care.

00:12:20.761 --> 00:12:22.179
IM JAE-I
IM SA-HYEONG'S SECOND SON

00:12:31.647 --> 00:12:33.649
THE TALE OF SUKHYANG

00:12:35.484 --> 00:12:37.361
SHIN HAE-RIM
THE QUEEN CONSORT'S NIECE

00:12:43.576 --> 00:12:45.411
