00:12:46.579 --> 00:12:47.705
It's too bland.

00:13:40.716 --> 00:13:41.550
Well.

00:13:41.634 --> 00:13:43.677
It looks like we're really destined.

00:13:44.261 --> 00:13:45.304
Pardon?

00:13:47.890 --> 00:13:49.642
I didn't expect to meet my fiancée here.

00:13:52.770 --> 00:13:54.813
Wait, are you…

00:13:54.897 --> 00:13:57.524
My father is the Chief Royal Secretary.

00:13:58.901 --> 00:14:02.071
