Pay your respects.

00:14:02.154 --> 00:14:04.323
Hello, I'm No-eul.

00:14:04.990 --> 00:14:07.117
And this woman here will be my concubine.

00:14:07.201 --> 00:14:09.119
No, maybe you already are.

00:14:10.704 --> 00:14:13.707
