I would be the consort,

00:14:14.917 --> 00:14:16.627
but I'll let you have that place.

00:14:19.338 --> 00:14:22.007
It's great to see my wives get along.

00:14:22.091 --> 00:14:24.593
Now that we're all here,
why don't we have a drink?

00:14:24.677 --> 00:14:25.970
We'll be family.

00:14:26.053 --> 00:14:27.513
That sounds lovely.

00:14:28.597 --> 00:14:32.977
