00:14:52.538 --> 00:14:56.750
everyone uses marriage
to secure wealth, honor, power,

00:14:56.834 --> 00:14:58.085
and higher status.

00:14:58.836 --> 00:15:01.296
So I might as well play for higher stakes.

00:15:01.380 --> 00:15:04.883
She's the Queen Consort's niece.
What could possibly be a higher stake?

00:15:05.884 --> 00:15:06.927
Something like…

00:15:08.929 --> 00:15:09.763
love.

00:15:12.516 --> 00:15:13.934
How typical.

00:15:14.018 --> 00:15:17.187
You highborn are all the same.

00:15:17.271 --> 00:15:19.940
Yes, I'm trying to put together
a typical charade.

00:15:21.650 --> 00:15:23.652
I have expectations to meet, after all.

00:15:28.907 --> 00:15:30.367
Stay healthy, okay?

00:15:31.410 --> 00:15:32.244
-Sir.
-Hello.

00:15:32.327 --> 00:15:34.538
I'm here to pick up the herbs I asked for.

00:15:34.621 --> 00:15:36.081
Sure. Just wait a second.

00:15:52.389 --> 00:15:54.349
I'm back, Young Master.

00:15:55.851 --> 00:15:58.312
-Wait, stop there.
-Yes?

00:15:59.855 --> 00:16:03.150
