wearing that physician's robe,

00:16:03.233 --> 00:16:04.943
reeking of my patients.

00:16:05.986 --> 00:16:07.529
I meant to change first,

00:16:07.613 --> 00:16:10.074
but things were hectic
at the Hyeminseo today.

00:16:10.783 --> 00:16:13.702
Do you think bringing home some money
suddenly makes you someone?

00:16:13.786 --> 00:16:15.037
But I'm your family's slave.

00:16:15.120 --> 00:16:16.622
-So what?
-What do you mean?

00:16:16.705 --> 00:16:18.415
Could a slave be someone?

00:16:20.834 --> 00:16:22.377
-Of course not.
-Exactly.

00:16:22.461 --> 00:16:23.712
Right.

00:16:25.506 --> 00:16:28.092
You're just being mean for no reason.

00:16:29.384 --> 00:16:31.386
How dare you talk back to me?

00:16:39.269 --> 00:16:40.562
Where did she go?

00:16:41.647 --> 00:16:42.523
Mother!

00:17:04.920 --> 00:17:07.506
-When did you get here?
-Just now.

00:17:08.799 --> 00:17:10.759
I know you're tired. Give it to me.

00:17:13.470 --> 00:17:17.432
Look at how dirty
the young master's socks are.

00:17:17.516 --> 00:17:19.852
Is he secretly seeing a woman
at night or what?

00:17:20.686 --> 00:17:24.314
Don't say that. He's not even married.

00:17:25.858 --> 00:17:27.943
I'll hang them.

00:17:28.026 --> 00:17:29.862
You go back and take the medicine.

00:17:29.945 --> 00:17:31.071
Let's do it together.

00:17:31.155 --> 00:17:34.199
Come on.
You need to take it while it's hot.

00:17:34.283 --> 00:17:35.576
Come on.

00:17:45.961 --> 00:17:48.005
HONG MIN-JIK
HONG EUN-JO'S FATHER

00:17:48.672 --> 00:17:50.090
Eun-jo, come to my room.

00:17:54.386 --> 00:17:56.305
What is it you wish to say, my lord?

00:17:57.764 --> 00:18:01.018
